this file contain project of invetory managemet System of a Shop Keeper to manage their items ...to see of how much items are sold out and how what amount of money of profitable 

I run a small retail store and to keep track of my inventory. can you create a software solution that helps me manage my products ,sales and inventory more efficientely?
FEATURES REQUESTED::--
PRODUCT MANAGEMENT : "I need a system where I can easily addd new products, update their detials , and remove outdated ones. "
STOCK TRACKING :: " Can the software track hoe many of eeach items I have instock and notify me when I need to restock?"
SALES RECORDING :: " I want to record eack sale and havee It automatically updted my invetory levels. "
REPORT GENERATOR :: " It would be great to generate reports showing what's selling well and what's low in stock. "
